<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf03deef0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s8719"><num value="8719">§ 8719.</num><heading> Period of effectiveness</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall be effective beginning with the 2008 crop year of each covered commodity through the 2012 crop year.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf03deef1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/110/234/tI/s1109">Pub. L. 110–234, title I, § 1109</ref>, <date date="2008-05-22">May 22, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/953">122 Stat. 953</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/246/s4/a">Pub. L. 110–246, § 4(a)</ref>, title I, § 1109, <date date="2008-06-18">June 18, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/1664">122 Stat. 1664</ref>, 1681.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idf03deef2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idf03deef3-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idf03deef4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/110/234">Pub. L. 110–234</ref> and <ref href="/us/pl/110/246">Pub. L. 110–246</ref> enacted identical sections. <ref href="/us/pl/110/234">Pub. L. 110–234</ref> was repealed by <ref href="/us/pl/110/246/s4/a">section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idf03deef5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idf03deef6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Enactment of this section and repeal of <ref href="/us/pl/110/234">Pub. L. 110–234</ref> by <ref href="/us/pl/110/246">Pub. L. 110–246</ref> effective <date date="2008-05-22">May 22, 2008</date>, the date of enactment of <ref href="/us/pl/110/234">Pub. L. 110–234</ref>, see <ref href="/us/pl/110/246/s4">section 4 of Pub. L. 110–246</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s8701">section 8701 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
